casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Kenneth Gerald COX, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 157680
COA: 340964 Supreme Court of Michigan. December 21, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the March 12, 2018 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
